    text: '<p><strong><span>World Winter Master Games 2020</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span>Innsbruck/AUT - 10.-19. Januar 2020</span></strong></p>\n\n<div>\n<div dir="auto"><span>Winter World Master Games Innsbruck 2020</span></div>\n<div dir="auto"><span><a tabindex="0" href="https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/spirittogether?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZW5sn8eaJEMoKnUuIVkeDj7GpmXvhIlj3CzVwqapnbZSpRglhtOS7lKjf3lwmqQsAAOGVbN0cqa6ia8oCw5mxRWRp4VPrG2d64A2iHjkq4IfbMb4ONFryXFIYGBHbcnd8BUiatHg0MNl-SEgKdKX8a-mYH_wzl4_kuK32vsjRYG_ets3TGEkyShzBZ-i4dEOvI&amp;__tn__=*NK-R">#spirittogether</a></span></div>\n\n<p><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div dir="auto"><span>Erfolgreicher Auftakt im Short Track bei den 1500m. Gundi holt Gold! Otto und Iris jeweils Silber.</span></div>\n<div dir="auto"><span>Morgen geht es weiter mit den 500m.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div dir="auto"><span>Auch morgen kann man die Rennen im livestream anschauen:</span></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div dir="auto"><span><a href="https://www.innsbruck2020.com/en/news/livestream-live-timing" target="_blank">https://www.innsbruck2020.com/en/news/livestream-live-timing</a></span></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div dir="auto"><span>Ergebnisse:</span></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div dir="auto"><span><a href="http://www.shorttracklive.info/index.php?comp=575&amp;m=0&amp;saison=15&amp;fbclid=IwAR3mtxAVs5zqcxA3LN_GmyAIuEtckRAaP44iBdAHo6xr7_UJYafxTisIb4I" target="_blank">http://www.shorttracklive.info/index.php?comp=575&amp;;m=0...</a></span></div>\n</div>',
